OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784467108
OL,3,CEngland v France: Three Lions prepare
OL,4,Cfor World Cup third-place play-off
OL,6,FFresh from a bruising defeat at the
OL,7,Fhands of Argentina, England will now
OL,8,Fattempt to park their semi-final agony
OL,9,Fand secure their best World Cup finish
OL,10,Fsince 1966.
OL,12,FThe Three Lions will play France in
OL,13,FMiami on Saturday for the third-place
OL,14,Fplay-off ` a fixture England have so
OL,15,Ffar never won.
OL,17,FEngland have lost their two previous
OL,18,Fthird-place play-offs in 1990 against
OL,19,Fhosts Italy, and in 2018 to Belgium in
OL,20,FRussia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
