CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784467108
OL,3,CEngland v France: Three Lions prepare
OL,4,Cfor World Cup third-place play-off
OL,6,FManager Thomas Tuchel nodded to this
OL,7,Fwhen facing a particularly pointed
OL,8,Fquestion on the eve of the bronze
OL,9,Fmedal game, suggesting that, despite
OL,10,FWednesday's 2-1 semi-final defeat,
OL,11,FEngland still have a chance to do
OL,12,Fsomething special.
OL,14,FAsked if it was fair that some of his
OL,15,Fdecisions in the defeat to Argentina
OL,16,Fwere described as cowardly, he said:
OL,17,F"Not at all. I don't receive them.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784467108
OL,3,CEngland v France: Three Lions prepare
OL,4,Cfor World Cup third-place play-off
OL,6,F"I don't read praise and I don't
OL,7,Fbelieve in praise and I don't believe
OL,8,Fin comments like this. If we win the
OL,9,Fgame tomorrow, we have the best result
OL,10,Fof a World Cup in 60 years. That's the
OL,11,Fperspective to it."
OL,13,FEngland captain Harry Kane and
OL,14,Fmidfielder Jude Bellingham, who have
OL,15,Feach scored six goals so far this
OL,16,FWorld Cup, could still win the Golden
OL,17,FBoot, an award for the tournament's
OL,18,Fhighest goal-scorer.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784467108
OL,3,CEngland v France: Three Lions prepare
OL,4,Cfor World Cup third-place play-off
OL,6,FThis will be a challenge, however,
OL,7,Fwith France's Kylian Mbappe and
OL,8,FArgentina's Lionel Messi both on eight
OL,9,Fgoals, each with one more match to
OL,10,Fplay.
OL,12,FWhat time is kick-off and where can I
OL,13,Fwatch it?
OL,15,FEngland will kick-off against France
OL,16,Fat the Miami Stadium on Saturday at
OL,17,F10pm BST.
OL,19,FYou can watch it on BBC One, or stream
OL,20,Fit online via BBC iPlayer, with pre-
OL,21,Fmatch coverage beginning at 9.30pm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
