PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784467108
OL,3,CEngland v France: Three Lions prepare
OL,4,Cfor World Cup third-place play-off
OL,6,FEngland's shot at the bronze medal
OL,7,Fcomes as Tuchel faces intense scrutiny
OL,8,Fover the decisions he made during
OL,9,FEngland's face-off with Argentina.
OL,11,FEven Donald Trump weighed in on the
OL,12,Fdebate, questioning the German coach's
OL,13,F"unusual" defensive use of Kane, who
OL,14,Frevealed last week that he had played
OL,15,Fa round of golf with the US President
OL,16,Faround 18 months ago in Florida.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784467108
OL,3,CEngland v France: Three Lions prepare
OL,4,Cfor World Cup third-place play-off
OL,6,F"You have a great player in England,
OL,7,Fwho I played golf with," Trump said in
OL,8,Fa press conference. "You know that,
OL,9,Fright? He is Harry, who's been
OL,10,Ffantastic.
OL,12,F"I think they perhaps made a mistake
OL,13,Fwhen they made him a defensive player.
OL,14,FWhat do I know about soccer? They took
OL,15,Fthe lead, and they took their best
OL,16,Fplayer and put him on defence."
OL,18,FGianni Infantino laughed alongside
OL,19,FTrump, with the FIFA president
OL,20,Fshrugging and then applauding his
OL,21,Fremarks.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@XO]pD@UOUtD@AOUxD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784467108
OL,3,CEngland v France: Three Lions prepare
OL,4,Cfor World Cup third-place play-off
OL,6,F"Look, what do I know about coaching?
OL,7,FBut that was a little unusual, but
OL,8,FHarry is a great guy, actually."
OL,10,FTuchel stood his ground when asked
OL,11,Fabout his approach at a press
OL,12,Fconference, saying: "To put it into
OL,13,Fcontext ` maybe it's worth to put it
OL,14,Finto context ` we lost the first
OL,15,Fofficial match together.
OL,17,F"Since 14 matches, it was our first
OL,18,Fdefeat. It was a painful one. We
OL,19,Fplayed in the semi-final against the
OL,20,Freigning world champions.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@`O]tD@UOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784467108
OL,3,CEngland v France: Three Lions prepare
OL,4,Cfor World Cup third-place play-off
OL,6,F"We were at 85 minutes 1-0 up. We
OL,7,Fplayed against the best player in the
OL,8,Fworld (Lionel Messi) and we lost 2-1,
OL,9,Fwhich is painful.
OL,11,F"We made our way to the semi-final.
OL,12,FWell deserved. We are one of the top
OL,13,Ffour nations and we wanted this place
OL,14,Fin the semi-final and we wanted more.
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784467108
OL,3,CEngland v France: Three Lions prepare
OL,4,Cfor World Cup third-place play-off
OL,6,F"We are heavily disappointed because
OL,7,Fwe wanted to play in the final. We
OL,8,Fbelieved we can do it.
OL,10,F"We built something to have this
OL,11,Fgenuine belief we can do it. We were
OL,12,Fdreaming about it. Still, I believe
OL,13,Fthat three other nations have almost
OL,14,Fexpectations to win the title. This is
OL,15,Fnot us.
OL,17,F"France, Spain, Argentina expect
OL,18,Falmost. They are on that level that
OL,19,Fthey expect to win. We are not there
OL,20,Fyet. There is still a gap to close and
OL,21,Fthis is what we will do.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784467108
OL,3,CEngland v France: Three Lions prepare
OL,4,Cfor World Cup third-place play-off
OL,6,F"This is what we will do from
OL,7,F(Saturday). We will we will not stop
OL,8,Fchasing. We will not stop hunting. We
OL,9,Fwill not stop challenging.
OL,11,F"We have a gap to close, like I said
OL,12,Fand we have things to improve in a
OL,13,Ffootball matter. This is the context,
OL,14,Fso I think it is in itself not a lot
OL,15,Fof room for drama.
OL,17,F"If drama is needed and if the blame
OL,18,Fgame needs to be played, OK, you can
OL,19,Fdo that, but I have the right to not
OL,20,Fengage in that."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
